  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Ruins_Guardian_Riddle
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Ruins Guardian
  _lines:
  - You stand among the bones of an age that wanted to live forever. They chased one thing above all else, and it unmade them, every one.
  - Two things you must wed. First, the unbreakable jewel the deep weeps under unbearable weight, clear and without flaw, the proudest thing the earth can harden.
  - Second, the golden draught that turns death from the door, the drink the dying have always begged for and never found.
  - Marry the flawless jewel to the deathless drink, and you will hold the prize that emptied this whole world. Make it, return to me, and the Fragment of Soul is yours.
